        <div class="am-g identify-title">
            <div class="am-u-lg-9">
                <span class="sy-bold">身份认证&nbsp;</span>
                <span class="sy-font-sm identy-no">还未认证，请先认证</span>
                <span class="sy-font-sm identy-yes">已认证</span>
